Results.ReviewText: Whether you need a coffee on the go, or at work, I always keep a sachet handy. I liked the original 3 in 1, but found I would always add another spoon of Nescafe. Now I don't need to as it is perfect - the balence is just right, and so rich. The packs of 5 make these so good value, and unlike a machine, the quality is always consistantly excellent, and no need to worry that all the milk has gone from the fridge. Top tip - always keep some at home when coming back from holiday so you don't need to worry about getting those provisions in. Just pop on the kettle!
Results.Title: Strong, sweet, and handsome in a cup!

Results.ReviewText: We picked up these for a recent trip to London for the Anniversary games, knowing it was going to be difficult to get a proper coffee on motorway services and at the venue and I'm glad I did! We simply ordered hot water and quickly added a sachet of NESCAFE 3 in 1 and joy to my taste buds a decent cup of coffee. These are perfect for day trips and long journeys if you can't guarantee the quality of your cup of coffee.
Results.Title: Essential travel item!

Results.ReviewText: If your after that ultimate coffee pick me up experience you need to try nescafe 3 in 1 strong.  Its a perfect morning pick me up and has the added benefit of being a sachet which saves time with having powdered milk already built in.  For some that are scepticle about an all in one coffee you need not be bothered, this coffee has all the distinct tastes of nescafe and more.
Results.Title: Wake me up juice

Results.ReviewText: These are marvellous, strong enough and sweet enough with the delicious Nescafé flavour, beautiful and handy.
Results.Title: Perfect size and shape for your pocket

Results.ReviewText: Anything that tastes like real coffee without all that faffing about with filters or machines just has to be good!
Results.Title: No faffing!
